data.description: Charming 2br/1ba Cal. Bungalow. Huge Back yard has storage room w/ fruit trees including Avocado/Orange. Long Driveway for up to 3 cars and oversized garage that can be use for workshop, hobbies or future Additional Dwelling Unit (ADU). New landscape.  Plenty of room for future additions. Close to shops and Freeways. Tax records show property as 1br/1ba.   Buyer and Buyer's agent to do due diligence. Standard Sale
